# Kandev Harness

Use the shared Kandev harness as the source of truth:

- Skills live under `.agents/skills/<name>/SKILL.md`.
- Source agent roles live under `.agents/agents/<name>.md`.
- Claude mirrors live under `.claude/agents/<name>.md`.
- Codex mirrors live under `.codex/agents/<name>.toml`.
- Cursor mirrors live under `.cursor/agents/<name>.md`.
- OpenCode mirrors live under `.opencode/agents/<name>.md`.

For harness edits, load `.agents/skills/harness-improvement/SKILL.md` and the relevant bundled references under `.agents/skills/harness-improvement/references/`. Use `references/platforms/` before external docs.

When updating a subagent role, update all requested project-local mirrors across `.agents/agents`, `.claude/agents`, `.codex/agents`, `.cursor/agents`, and `.opencode/agents` unless the user scopes the request to one platform.
